NAME
    Dancer::Plugin::Database::Core - Shared core for D1 and D2 Database
    plugins

SYNOPSIS
    This module should not be used directly. It is a shared library for
    Dancer::Plugin::Database and Dancer2::Plugin::Database modules.

METHODS
  database
    Implements the `database' keyword.

AUTHOR
    David Precious, `<davidp at preshweb.co.uk>'

BUGS
    Please report any bugs or feature requests to
    `bug-dancer-plugin-database-core at rt.cpan.org', or through the web
    interface at
    http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/ReportBug.html?Queue=Dancer-Plugin-Database-Co
    re. I will be notified, and then you'll automatically be notified of
    progress on your bug as I make changes.

